videos.description: Carter Stanley throws a pass to the middle of the field and is intercepted by Antwuan Davis who returns it for a 16-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Longhorns pick-6 gives extends lead

videos.description: Toneil Carter takes the hand-off and jukes three defenders to score a 23-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Longhorns' Carter showing off impressive moves for TD

videos.description: Carter Stanley completely misreads his receiver and throws it right to Jason Hall who returns it 25-yards.
videos.headline: Texas defense gets 3rd int of the game

videos.description: S. Ehlinger pass,to K. Moore for 8 yds for a TD, (M. Becker KICK)
videos.headline: Longhorns' Brewer TD catch gives them huge lead

videos.description: Carter Stanley finds Earl Bostick who makes a leaping grab for an 8-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Kansas's Stanley-Bostick TD cuts into lead

videos.description: Lil' Jordan Humphrey takes the wildcat option and runs it in for a 1-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Texas WR Humphrey takes direct snap in for TD

videos.description: Carter Stanley throws the ball in the end zone but Antwuan Davis picks it off right before halftime.
videos.headline: Texas CB Davis gets 2nd pick at crucial time

videos.description: Tom Herman says his team isn't playing defense to their potential and needs to convert third downs on offense.
videos.headline: Herman thinks Texas needs to be better in all facets of the game

videos.description: Tyler Patrick is trying to block for Steven Sims Jr. on a pass play but his leg gets rolled into causing a  injury.
videos.headline: Kansas WR Patrick is carted off field with injury

videos.description: Shane Buechele misreads his receiver and throws the interception to Hasan Defense who returns it for a  10-yard gain.
videos.headline: Kansas gets much needed Int

videos.description: Shane Buechele throws a short pass to Lil' Jordan Humphrey and he completely jumps over a defender for a 16-yard gain.
videos.headline: Texas WR Humphrey hurdles defender

videos.description: Chris Warren III takes the direct snap in for a 1-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Texas rush TD extends lead late in the 4th
